{"name": "reward-K-tracksharp", "warm_start": "best", "variant": "walk-biped-tdmpc", "overrides": {"rewards.feet_slide.weight": -0.12, "rewards.upright_bonus.weight": 0.4, "rewards.stand_walk.params.tracking_std": 0.15}, "notes": "Keep idx6 shape; sharpen velocity-tracking (tracking_std 0.25->0.15) so the gated core reward pays much more for ACTUALLY matching the commanded 0.3 m/s. Direct forward-speed lever that is NOT move_weight (poison). Final reward-param probe before the curriculum fix becomes the only path."}
